title: 关于空岛插件
author: @Later
txt_content:
怎么让空岛变成海岛
求详细教程

replies.txt_content:
根据空岛插件里的sealevel参数与islandlevel参数，似乎你把这两个参数都改成50就可以把空岛改成海岛
  # Sea level height (don't changes this mid-game unless you delete the world)
   # Minimum is 0, which means you are playing skyblock!
   # If sea level is less than about 10 players will drop right through it
   # if it exists. Makes for an interesting variation on skyblock.
   sealevel: 50

   # Island level - the height of the island.
   # Lowest level is 5
   islandlevel: 50

replies.author: 冰星
replies.txt_content: 空岛和海岛是两套不同的插件
把空岛插件换成海岛插件

replies.author: 零尘233
replies.txt_content:
虽然是同一个作者写的 引用的config文件也是相同的
但由于核心代码不同
所以无法达到你要的在空岛内部换成海岛
只能跟楼上说的更换插件

(当然你要是问我如果要保留玩家的空岛数据，我打死都不会回)
